    <section class="kgm-box front-box">
     <img src="/resources/images/karl-maeser.jpg;jsessionid=2728C463AE6E20A289B6B4BD94FF505F"/>
     <article>
      <p>
       All students applying to a Church Educational System school, which includes
					Brigham Young University, Brigham Young University-Hawaii, Brigham Young University-Idaho,
					and LDS Business College, are required to have an Ecclesiastical Endorsement.
      </p>
      <p>
       Students need to select "Student" below and follow the instructions before meeting with ecclesiastical leader.
      </p>
      <p>
       Leaders can access a queue of students seeking endorsement by selecting "Leader" and following the instructions.
      </p>
     </article>
    </section>
